The Glenn Beck Program



Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
      The Glenn Beck Program - 12/13/13Friday, December 13, 2013 11:38 AM





Glenn just had his annual company Christmas party at his house
    and there were some extra unexpected guests, Glenn explains.

  Also, after a holiday hiatus, More-On Trivia is back,
         this week it's Dallas vs Green Bay.

  Plus, why does the Left fear article V in the Constitution, Glenn explains,
      and new details emerge about the fake sign language translator from Mandela's memorial,
        and they are shocking.
